# Challenges With Microservices Architecture

==================================================

---------------------
## 1. Bounded Context
----------------------

Deciding

• How many microservices
• Which functionality belongs to which service

Requires strong domain understanding.

---------------------------
## 2. Repeated Configuration
---------------------------

Every microservice requires configuration such as

• Database
• Security
• Kafka
• Logging
• Monitoring

Configuration duplication may occur.

-------------------------=
## 3. Service Visibility
-------------------------

In large systems it becomes difficult to know

```
Which service provides which functionality
```

To solve this we use

• Service Registry
• Documentation
• Monitoring tools

